{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/TransparencyTBerserk.gif?t=1730111123\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/AboutSteam.png?t=1730111123\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Leshy Prelude is a <strong>20-30 minute action-adventure experience</strong>. It contains graphics inspired by the rendering limitations of PSX along with gun-play mechanics that encourage puzzle-solving/timing with a mix of movement, reaction times, and aiming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you enjoy boomer shooters with a mix of story elements, you'll more than likely enjoy this for the challenge and intrigue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/FeaturesSteam.png?t=1730111123\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A mysterious and gripping story as you uncover the horrors of the forest.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> FPS Action with (relatively) fast-paced gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Mechanics that work in-tandem to encourage quick-thinking, precise timing, and satisfying execution.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Controller Support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Classic PSX-inspired graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A State-of-the-art investigative licking experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Steam Achievements</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/ProfileSteam.png?t=1730111123\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Profiles and some background about the characters within Leshy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p cl